Tajmaɛt n umenɣi ɣef yixef nndama tameqqrant, iqublen qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tnezduɣt-nni armi d ass i deg yețwarfed ɣer igenni.
Meɛna m'ara d-yaf wemɣṛent acḥal d abrid n twaɣit s tmes tețfeǧǧiǧ, mkul aṭan : acḥal n tikkal i ɛerḍeɣ a n-ruɣ iman-nsent deg waṭas n yedrimen, acḥal aț-țeṛɣay tmes i d-yețțaken tudert-nsen.
Ur nezmir ara a nxiḍ tafaweț tajḍiṭ i uceṭṭiḍ aqdim, axaṭer tafaweț-nni tajḍiṭ aț-țejbed aceṭṭiḍ-nni aqdim, acerrig-nni ad innerni.
Bdan ṭeggiṛen aɣebbaṛ ɣef yiqeṛṛay-nsen, llan yid-sen illan țid imeɛdazen, bɣan ad sɛeddin lweqt-nni di lexṣaṣ, a d-uɣalen ɣer webrid n Sidi Ṛebbi.
Di mkul lweqt ilaq aț-țeččem aț-țeẓẓuɣ di texxamt, aț-țeẓẓuɣ di texxamt-agi i țɣawseṛ ɣuṛ-es.
